439
00:46:09,522 --> 00:46:17,664
So I think we have to we have to balance the operational aspects of there being enough people in the building to have school.

440
00:46:18,284 --> 00:46:22,425
But also, I don't want to see us sort of

441
00:46:23,125 --> 00:46:32,950
move away from those observances for the folks in our community who are used to not being seen and not feeling seen.

442
00:46:33,090 --> 00:46:41,534
