443
00:46:43,477 --> 00:46:46,718
we if we if we don't feel seen we cannot belong.

444
00:46:47,278 --> 00:46:52,960
And I know that our teachers work really hard to make students feel seen every single day.

445
00:46:53,000 --> 00:47:01,423
And I think this is like a district wide sort of statement about feeling seen that we have to be like really mindful of.

446
00:47:02,921 --> 00:47:19,675
And then I think my last comment would be I would love to see there be some sort of collaborative working group like really collaborative out in the open in public for people to participate in where we talk more broadly about the problems of the calendar because I think

447
00:47:21,932 --> 00:47:25,295
There are lots of problems of the calendar, depending on who you talk to.

448
00:47:25,675 --> 00:47:30,219
And there's the way that these things have always been, or they have been for a long time.

449
00:47:30,239 --> 00:47:36,564
And then there's the practical realities of caregiving that continue to evolve and become more stressful for families.

450
00:47:37,144 --> 00:47:42,508
So I would like to see some sort of collaborative conversation happen at some point about the calendar.

451
00:47:42,548 --> 00:47:47,953
And I mean, you could throw start times, you could throw all kinds of things in there, all of which, by the way, are sort of

