454
00:48:07,988 --> 00:48:23,463
But I think really when when caregivers and teachers collaborate together there's really really powerful outcomes for students and I think we should consider doing something like that as we talk about the broader calendar implications for our community going forward.

455
00:48:23,943 --> 00:48:24,263
Thank you.

